✅ **Build succeeds with 0 warnings, 0 errors.** Here's a summary of all fixes applied:

### Fixes applied to this project

1. **`EfApp.csproj`** — TFM `net8.0` → `net9.0`, packages `8.0.0` → `9.0.0`, added `<Publish>true</Publish>` to Design package (fixes EF tools with SDK 9.0.200+)

2. **`AppDbContext.cs`** — Replaced `DateTime.UtcNow` in `HasData` with a fixed constant. Non-deterministic values cause EF Core 9 to throw "*pending model changes*" on every `Migrate()` call.

3. **`MigrationRunner.cs`** — Removed the explicit `BeginTransaction`/`ExecutionStrategy` wrapper around `Migrate()`. EF Core 9 manages its own transactions and throws if wrapped in a user transaction.

### Required fixes for your Cosmos DB project

Apply these in your Cosmos DB `DbContext.OnModelCreating`:

```csharp
// (A) Preserve old discriminator property name (default changed to "$type")
modelBuilder.Entity<YourEntity>().HasDiscriminator<string>("Discriminator");

// (B) Preserve old compound id format ("EntityType|KeyValue")
modelBuilder.Entity<YourEntity>().HasRootDiscriminatorInJsonId(true);

// (C) Replace all sync calls — Cosmos provider now throws on sync I/O
//     SaveChanges()  → await SaveChangesAsync()
//     .ToList()      → await .ToListAsync()
//     .First()       → await .FirstAsync()
```
